==English==

===Adjective===
'''anthropophilic'''

# Preferring [[human]] beings to other animals, such as a mosquito or a dermatophyte.  It is especially alluding to: 1) bloodsucking arthropods, denoting the preference of a parasite for the human host as a source of blood or tissues over an animal host; and 2) dermatophytic fungi which grow preferentially on humans.

